Lindsay Lindley (amụrụ na 10 June 1989) bụ onye Naijirịa na-agba ọsọ nke amụrụ na America bụ onye ọkachamara na 100m hurdles. Ọ nọchitere anya Naijirịa na 2015 World Championships in Athletics mgbe Athletics Federation of Nigeria họpụtara ya. N'afọ 2015, o kwuru na ọ bụ ọla nchara na 100 mita hurdles na 2015 All-Africa Games.
